  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>Defunctive\n        music</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>From William Shakespeare's \"The\n        Phoenix and the Turtle.\" The whole stanza reads:\n        \"</font>Let the priest in surplice white, / That\n        defunctive music can, / Be the death-divining swan, /\n        Lest the requiem lack his right.\"</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Phoenix_WS.htm\">\"The\n                Phoenix and the Turtle\"</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Phoenix_WS.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font>\"The Phoenix\" and\n                \"Burbank\"</font></td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
